NK075(bu)001:1: // tsi t+ta bi n+d+hu u pa de sha n+aa ma bi ha ra ti sma /
NK075(bu)001:4: // thugs kyi thigs pa'i man ngag ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK075(bu)001:7: tsit+ta bin+d+hu u pa de sha n+aa ma /
NK075(bu)001:9: thugs kyi thigs pa'i man ngag ces bya ba /
NK075(bu)001:10: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' gtso //
NK075(bu)001:11: kun mkhyen rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK075(bu)001:12: 'khor lo snying po ston mdzad la //
NK075(bu)001:13: gnyis med yid kyis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK075(bu)001:14: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rdo rje sems //
NK075(bu)001:15: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud dag las //
NK075(bu)001:16: rin chen bcud thugs skal ldan phyir //
NK075(bu)001:17: legs par bsdus te bstan par bya //
NK075(bu)001:18: rgya mtsho las ni chu thugs bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:19: ye shes rgya mtsho thugs kyi thugs //
NK075(bu)001:20: mi 'jigs phung po ji bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:21: ye shes thugs kyi bcu gsum po //
NK075(bu)001:22: rang bzhin bde gshegs gdul bya yi //
NK075(bu)001:23: snang ba gsum gyi ngo bo la //
NK075(bu)001:24: rgyud kyi dbye ba rnam par bzhag /
NK075(bu)001:25: gcig la gsum gyi ngo bo yang //
NK075(bu)001:27: des na snang ba bzhi dag tu //
NK075(bu)001:28: lung rigs kun nas gsal bar bshad //
NK075(bu)001:29: yan lag rdo rje rnam bzhi po //
NK075(bu)001:30: thog mar bstan pa'i byang chub sems //
NK075(bu)001:31: 'gro ba mang po'i sems rgyud rnams //
NK075(bu)001:32: log rtog ngo bo rgyu rkyen gyis //
NK075(bu)001:33: tha dad du sa gser bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:34: rang byung ye shes tha dad med //
NK075(bu)001:35: de yang 'ching grol gnyis ka'i bdag /
NK075(bu)001:36: me long dwangs ba'i g.ya' bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:37: phan tshun spangs pa med pa la //
NK075(bu)001:38: byis pas gzhi dang rten zhes smra //
NK075(bu)001:39: mkhas pas lhun grub smra bsam 'das //
NK075(bu)001:40: 'di skad gsang ba'i rgyud nyid las //
NK075(bu)001:41: gshegs sku sgyu mar snang ba dang //
NK075(bu)001:42: log rtog sgyu mar snang ba gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:43: rigs dang rgyud du brtag tu med //
NK075(bu)001:44: gzhi rtsa med de rang bzhin stong //
NK075(bu)001:45: rigs dang kha dog dbyibs med las //
NK075(bu)001:46: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad snang //
NK075(bu)001:47: yang ni sgyu 'phrul dra ba las //
NK075(bu)001:48: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK075(bu)001:49: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK075(bu)001:50: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK075(bu)001:51: gsungs pas rang bzhin rgyud nyid ni //
NK075(bu)001:52: ma rig ye shes tha dad min //
NK075(bu)001:53: nam mkha' dwangs kyang sprin gyi gnas //
NK075(bu)001:54: dwangs rigs can gyi 'gro ba ltar //
NK075(bu)001:55: rtog sems mi mthun sems nyid du //
NK075(bu)001:56: gcig pas rang bzhin thug med pas //
NK075(bu)001:58: ne le'i rkyal pas rin chen char //
NK075(bu)001:59: rgyal po yang dag don gyi gnas //
NK075(bu)001:60: bram ze dam pa tsi bi ra //
NK075(bu)001:61: dbul po tan+ti'i grong khyer dang //
NK075(bu)001:63: gdol ba'i grong du rin po che //
NK075(bu)001:64: sna tshogs rin chen phal pa lnga //
NK075(bu)001:65: bye tshul gram pa lhad ras hrul //
NK075(bu)001:66: sha khrag rus pa rin chen sil //
NK075(bu)001:67: gcig la so sor snang ba bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:68: spyod yul tha dad snang ba yang //
NK075(bu)001:69: rang sems rkyen gyi snang ba tsam //
NK075(bu)001:70: ngo bo rigs rgyud phyogs med pas //
NK075(bu)001:71: de la des sgyur snang btub bo //
NK075(bu)001:72: spyir ni log rtog bsam yas pa //
NK075(bu)001:73: ye nas yod pa ma yin te //
NK075(bu)001:74: so sos 'dzin rtog bag chags kyis //
NK075(bu)001:75: rang gi bsgrib shing rtag tu 'khor //
NK075(bu)001:76: 'di skad gsungs pa'ang thog med nas //
NK075(bu)001:77: sems las logs su ma gyur cing //
NK075(bu)001:78: rgyu rkyen las kyis glo bur ba'i //
NK075(bu)001:79: spyod yul snang dus thog mtha' med //
NK075(bu)001:80: sems rgyud gnyis kun lhun grub pa //
NK075(bu)001:81: nor bu rin chen lta bu la //
NK075(bu)001:83: phan tshun spangs par gang 'dod med //
NK075(bu)001:84: dred mos rtsi 'bras byabs pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:85: gsang ba'i don mchog ga la yod //
NK075(bu)001:86: kun nas nyon mongs rnam par byang //
NK075(bu)001:87: ye nas ngo bo yod yin na //
NK075(bu)001:88: nyon mongs yongs spang byang bsgrub med //
NK075(bu)001:89: so so'i rang bzhin nges shes na //
NK075(bu)001:90: yang dag lam gyis bcos su med //
NK075(bu)001:91: de gsungs phyir na rgyur gnas pa //
NK075(bu)001:92: shes blo gzhi zhes gnyis su smra //
NK075(bu)001:93: bsam pa chos nyid de bzhin te //
NK075(bu)001:94: de la yod pa de la med //
NK075(bu)001:95: phyogs su rtogs pa bden zhe na //
NK075(bu)001:96: de dang de la 'brel med pas //
NK075(bu)001:97: nam yang sngon bzhin bden pa min //
NK075(bu)001:98: mi rtog pa yi sems rgyud ldan //
NK075(bu)001:99: thams cad dag ces bya ba yang //
NK075(bu)001:100: dngos po bsal dag ma yin te //
NK075(bu)001:101: snang spyod nyid na rnam par dag /
NK075(bu)001:102: gsungs pas log rtog spang du med //
NK075(bu)001:103: sprin dang bzhin tshon snang ba'i tshe //
NK075(bu)001:104: rang bzhin stong par ngang gis gnas //
NK075(bu)001:105: gang dag rgyu yi theg pa pas //
NK075(bu)001:106: kun tu rtog pa don dam la //
NK075(bu)001:107: yod na nges tshig med dogs pas //
NK075(bu)001:108: dwangs shing gsal dag gang 'dod pa //
NK075(bu)001:109: bsam pa dag la de yod ces //
NK075(bu)001:110: so sor ston pa rtog pa'i blos //
NK075(bu)001:111: dag pa mnyam gnyis gnyis med dag /
NK075(bu)001:112: ldog pas phye ba ji bzhin sgrar //
NK075(bu)001:113: gang zhen sgrub pa'i phyogs 'dod pa //
NK075(bu)001:114: gam ga da rdza'i mi bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:115: spyod yul bral la 'dod pas gdungs //
NK075(bu)001:116: ye shes ngang la gnyis rtog bslus //
NK075(bu)001:117: lhun grub ngang la phe rngam zad //
NK075(bu)001:118: gang shes mi gtsang spos dri dang //
NK075(bu)001:119: tsher ma'i nang nas na bza' bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:120: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK075(bu)001:121: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK075(bu)001:122: yod las btsal ba sgros gtags te //
NK075(bu)001:123: med las btsal na skur btab 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:124: yod med gnyis las btsal byas na //
NK075(bu)001:125: de ni lung du ma bstan 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:126: de gsungs phyir na rang rig la //
NK075(bu)001:127: yod med dgag sgrub blun po'i blo //
NK075(bu)001:128: de bas sems kyi de kho na //
NK075(bu)001:129: kun tu btags dang gzhan gyi dbang //
NK075(bu)001:130: yongs su grub pa'i bye brag tu //
NK075(bu)001:131: bya ba de dang de med de //
NK075(bu)001:132: de ni smra bsam med mi 'jog /
NK075(bu)001:133: rang byung kun la rgyas btab pas //
NK075(bu)001:134: rang bzhin kun dang dbyer med la //
NK075(bu)001:135: med pa bzhi ltar gnas pa'ang med //
NK075(bu)001:136: bden pa rnam gnyis dbyer med phyir //
NK075(bu)001:137: dga' sgrub med pa'i smra bsam grol //
NK075(bu)001:138: thams cad ye shes snang ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:139: mi mthun 'dus pas rtag tu med //
NK075(bu)001:140: yid bzhin shing ltar gnas pa la //
NK075(bu)001:141: ji bzhin sgra ru rtog pa 'khrul //
NK075(bu)001:142: bden pa gnyis su med pa yang //
NK075(bu)001:143: mkha' dang gzha' sprin gnas pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:144: snang stong kun tu rang gsal ba //
NK075(bu)001:145: rang bzhin ngang gis snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)001:146: bdag dang gzhan du ma brtags par //
NK075(bu)001:147: so sor snang bzhin mthun pa'i gzugs //
NK075(bu)001:148: de lta bu yi ngang du snang //
NK075(bu)001:149: de gsungs lung gis bgrod kyang sla //
NK075(bu)001:150: phyin ci log nyid yang dag ste //
NK075(bu)001:151: ma rig pa nyid ye shes gsal //
NK075(bu)001:152: nyon mongs sdug bsngal byang chub mchog /
NK075(bu)001:153: de gsungs don gyis de 'phos med //
NK075(bu)001:154: mar me'i dus na mun ldan pa //
NK075(bu)001:155: blun pos mun snang re mos mthong //
NK075(bu)001:156: mkhas pas ngo bo ris med lta //
NK075(bu)001:157: 'khor ba chos nyid de bzhin no //
NK075(bu)001:158: spangs pa med pas kun bral ba //
NK075(bu)001:159: pan+da r+ai ka lta bu'i don //
NK075(bu)001:160: lam dang 'bras bu chos tshang ba //
NK075(bu)001:163: rang bzhin gyi rgyud snang ba'i le'u ste dang po'o //
NK075(bu)001:165: // 'khrul gzhi tshul dang rang bzhin gyi //
NK075(bu)001:166: sdom des nges par shes par bya //
NK075(bu)001:167: drug gi 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK075(bu)001:168: sems nyid nor bu rin po che //
NK075(bu)001:169: ji ltar sems par snang ba la //
NK075(bu)001:170: 'khrul gzhi yod med sgro skur med //
NK075(bu)001:171: sgro 'dog dbang gyur gang zag rnams //
NK075(bu)001:172: sems nyid dmigs su med pa las //
NK075(bu)001:173: dngos po rang rgyud gzhir smra ba //
NK075(bu)001:174: de ni rigs rgyud rtag par lhung //
NK075(bu)001:175: skur pa pa ni lhun grub la //
NK075(bu)001:176: de dang bsam pa so sor rtog /
NK075(bu)001:177: de la de ni mi srid bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:178: gzhi la ye nas med ces smra //
NK075(bu)001:179: zhen blo'i ngo la yod do zhes //
NK075(bu)001:180: skur pa gang yin chad ltar ba //
NK075(bu)001:181: de dang de gnyis tha dad cing //
NK075(bu)001:183: la las log pa gnyis med las //
NK075(bu)001:184: snang smra lhan cig med pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:185: brten pa mi gos gzhir mi btub //
NK075(bu)001:186: rgyu rkyen spang ba rigs pa min //
NK075(bu)001:187: don nyid yod med rigs med las //
NK075(bu)001:188: de yi rgyu rkyen rang bzhin pas //
NK075(bu)001:189: sman gyi phan gnod ji bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:190: thams cad ma lus rgyu gcig las //
NK075(bu)001:191: mi mthun khyad par so sor snang //
NK075(bu)001:192: de gsungs phyir na rkyen gyis phye //
NK075(bu)001:193: lung las kyang ni 'di skad gsungs //
NK075(bu)001:194: rgyud drug 'khor ba'i lus snang ba //
NK075(bu)001:195: rnam rtog mthun pa'i las snang ngo //
NK075(bu)001:196: sku mchog rdo rje 'od snang ba //
NK075(bu)001:197: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK075(bu)001:198: de bas sems kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK075(bu)001:199: mthong ba dag dang ma dag gis //
NK075(bu)001:200: phye bas spyod yul so sor snang //
NK075(bu)001:201: de la ma spangs mi dmigs phyir //
NK075(bu)001:202: mtshon pa yod med dogs pa'ang med //
NK075(bu)001:203: dgag pa med pas blang med phyir //
NK075(bu)001:204: mtha' yi gzhung du bsgrub mi dgos //
NK075(bu)001:205: ma rig mtshungs par ldan pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:206: dus gsum rgyun du don mthong med //
NK075(bu)001:207: mig gis mig bzhin de lta bas //
NK075(bu)001:208: gnyis snang snga phyir longs btangs nor //
NK075(bu)001:209: sdom ni dus dang rgyud rkyen dang //
NK075(bu)001:210: tshul dang ngo bor rang bzhin nyes //
NK075(bu)001:211: tan+t+ra nyid las gsungs pa ni //
NK075(bu)001:212: thog ma med nas sems yan btang //
NK075(bu)001:213: phyir ci log la 'jol nyog spyod //
NK075(bu)001:214: gal te ma byung byung gyur na //
NK075(bu)001:216: ngo bo nyid dang mtshungs pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:217: lhan cig byed dang nyer len 'phel //
NK075(bu)001:218: rang byung rigs rgyud med pa nyid //
NK075(bu)001:219: de yi snang phyir tan+t+ra las //
NK075(bu)001:220: sngang gsungs don gyi dang po'i rgyud //
NK075(bu)001:221: ngo bo nyid kyang gzhan du min //
NK075(bu)001:222: sngon gyi me long rnam gnyis ltar //
NK075(bu)001:223: gdod nas ldan pas gnyis med pa'o //
NK075(bu)001:224: kun tu btangs pa rnam gnyis po //
NK075(bu)001:225: goms pas mnyam du 'byung ba gsum //
NK075(bu)001:226: de yi rkyen gyis brtas bslangs pa //
NK075(bu)001:227: 'od ma lta bur phyi mar snang //
NK075(bu)001:228: khams gsum 'di na gnas pa kun //
NK075(bu)001:229: dkar nag bcu yi dang po ste //
NK075(bu)001:230: tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi bsam gtan bzhis //
NK075(bu)001:231: bcu bdun gnas ris spyod yul snang //
NK075(bu)001:232: snyoms par 'jug pa'i mthun ldan na //
NK075(bu)001:233: rtse mo bzhi yi spyod yul snang //
NK075(bu)001:234: rgyud lnga'i lam du dug lnga ste /
NK075(bu)001:236: phyi nang 'khor lo'i gnas bskyar ba'ang //
NK075(bu)001:237: khams gsum cha yis nges pa med //
NK075(bu)001:238: 'khrul rtog brtan pa'i spyod yul ni //
NK075(bu)001:239: so so'i phyi nang snod bcud dang //
NK075(bu)001:240: lus dang longs spyod tshe dang las //
NK075(bu)001:241: bde sdug bar ma tha dad pa'o //
NK075(bu)001:242: sgyu la bslus pa'i mi bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:243: nor ba'i spyod yul rang bzhin snang //
NK075(bu)001:244: srid rtsa'i nyes pa bdag las phyir //
NK075(bu)001:245: sdug bsngal myong zhing lam dang bral //
NK075(bu)001:246: de lta'i dus na rgyud nyid las //
NK075(bu)001:247: nam mkha'i dbyings ni bsam yas par //
NK075(bu)001:248: nyi zla gza' skar mtshan mo glog 'gyu dang //
NK075(bu)001:249: gzha' tshon sprin mang sna tshogs 'khrugs gyur kyang //
NK075(bu)001:250: nam mkha'i dbyings las 'gyur zhing nyams pa med //
NK075(bu)001:251: mi dmigs chos kyi dbyings ni bsam yas par //
NK075(bu)001:252: sku gsung thugs yon phrin las rmad byung dang //
NK075(bu)001:253: 'jig rten gtso mchog sna tshogs rnam mang yang //
NK075(bu)001:254: chos kyi dbyings las 'gyur zhing nyams pa med //
NK075(bu)001:255: de dang bral ba'i spyan bzang rnams //
NK075(bu)001:256: de dang de ni de nyid dang //
NK075(bu)001:257: gzhan du brjod du med ces smra //
NK075(bu)001:258: gnyis su med pas kun tu brel //
NK075(bu)001:260: 'khrul pa'i snang ba'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o //
NK075(bu)001:262: // rang bzhin las kyis phye ba yis //
NK075(bu)001:263: chos nyid bya byed rigs pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:264: mos snod bcud sbyar bsam yas pa //
NK075(bu)001:265: gdul bya'i snang ba zhes su brjod //
NK075(bu)001:266: de dang de rkyen de de yis //
NK075(bu)001:267: ji bzhin de bzhin mngon byed pa //
NK075(bu)001:268: rim pa bzhi dang lnga pa yi //
NK075(bu)001:269: brgyud stegs nyid du sbyor ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:270: 'di skad rgyud las gsungs pa ni //
NK075(bu)001:271: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK075(bu)001:272: theg pa gcig gis 'bras bur gnas //
NK075(bu)001:273: gcig la gnyis dang gnyis la drug /
NK075(bu)001:274: phyin ci log pa mos sogs pa //
NK075(bu)001:275: rang bzhin grub mthar 'jug pa gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:276: mtha' ma log dang ma log pa //
NK075(bu)001:277: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtog /
NK075(bu)001:278: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK075(bu)001:279: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba dang //
NK075(bu)001:280: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK075(bu)001:281: ces gsungs thugs rje'i sar gyur pa //
NK075(bu)001:282: so so'i snang rkyen bsam yas na'ang //
NK075(bu)001:283: mchog rkyen rgyud ni rnam gsum ste //
NK075(bu)001:284: gsang ba'i rigs gnyis lta bu yi //
NK075(bu)001:285: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rdo rje sems //
NK075(bu)001:286: spyi gcod sngon bzhin bstan gsum pa //
NK075(bu)001:287: rkyen 'di yi ge las skal snod //
NK075(bu)001:288: shes rab 'brel bzhes yod pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:289: dbang pos phye ba'i thugs thigs gsum //
NK075(bu)001:290: dang po mtshon pa'i ming gsum ldan //
NK075(bu)001:291: nges pa'i lung ni sgyu d+r+wa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:292: dngos po gnyis pa'i legs snang ba //
NK075(bu)001:293: bden pas 'brel ba gnyis su med //
NK075(bu)001:294: de nyid gnyis med 'jig bral ba //
NK075(bu)001:295: gsal brtan las kyi lha yi ming //
NK075(bu)001:296: de ni bstan pa'i dngos gzhi bas //
NK075(bu)001:297: spyi lung nges pa gnyis pa'i mtshan //
NK075(bu)001:298: bstan brtags dka' ba'i don bcud de //
NK075(bu)001:299: bzhi yis kun la mi snang ba //
NK075(bu)001:300: kho na nyid gsum ldan bden pa'i //
NK075(bu)001:301: ming gis mtshon las ltag pa'i don //
NK075(bu)001:302: tshig rgyas kyis kyang mtshon mi nus //
NK075(bu)001:303: de bas gzhon nu'i rtog pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:304: yi ge bsdus pas don rgyas pa //
NK075(bu)001:305: brda phrad tha snyad bsdus pa yin //
NK075(bu)001:306: gsum pa'i ming la mos pa'i blos //
NK075(bu)001:307: so sor 'dod la shes rab thabs //
NK075(bu)001:308: nyi mas mdzes pa'i rin chen ltar //
NK075(bu)001:309: tshig gi sgron mes shes rab phye //
NK075(bu)001:310: 'bring la snang ba mched pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:311: rgyas par bye brag thigs par shar //
NK075(bu)001:312: rang bzhin las kyi snang gyur pa //
NK075(bu)001:313: bgrod thabs gnyis su yan lag rkyen //
NK075(bu)001:314: thog ma bar dang tha ma yul //
NK075(bu)001:315: lnga dang gnyis dang gnyis bstan to //
NK075(bu)001:316: dang po'i yul la rgyu rkyen dang //
NK075(bu)001:317: bzhi bcu gtad pas rdzogs pa yin //
NK075(bu)001:318: thabs dang shes rab rgyu yang ni //
NK075(bu)001:319: snga ma'i ston pa gnas 'khor sdud //
NK075(bu)001:320: dus bstan drug gnas rin chen sgrom //
NK075(bu)001:321: gsang ba'i 'og min gnas kyis phye //
NK075(bu)001:322: yi ge bzhi yis shes par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:323: gsang ba'i tshad ma gnyis dang 'brel //
NK075(bu)001:324: blo gros rgyu la thun mong mchog /
NK075(bu)001:325: bla ma rang sems ye shes che //
NK075(bu)001:326: gzhi dang las kyi gnas ston pa //
NK075(bu)001:327: ye shes mang po shes pa'i bdag /
NK075(bu)001:328: bstan pa'i bcud thugs bsdus dngos po //
NK075(bu)001:329: bkrag gsal lung la dus bzhi mnyam //
NK075(bu)001:330: de la de yod de rtogs 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:331: thun mong ba la mtshan gnyis gzugs //
NK075(bu)001:332: ston pa rang byung rdo rje 'dzin //
NK075(bu)001:333: rgyal tshab rgyud nas skyes bu gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:334: rang bzhin dus gsum chos las min //
NK075(bu)001:335: longs spyod chen po ku na tu zhal //
NK075(bu)001:336: mos pa'i mtshan grangs rdul snyed la //
NK075(bu)001:337: mnyam gzhag longs spyod chos ston pa //
NK075(bu)001:338: ming bzhi ldan pa'i skyil krung gnas //
NK075(bu)001:339: de yi brten pa rang bzhin gzhi //
NK075(bu)001:340: chos dbyings 'og min gsang ba na //
NK075(bu)001:341: lhan cig 'dus pa rin chen khang //
NK075(bu)001:342: ma spangs lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:343: dbyibs tshad rtse mo glo 'bur dang //
NK075(bu)001:345: bdag nyid dang ni bdag po dang //
NK075(bu)001:346: logs mgul sgo dang phyi yi rgyan //
NK075(bu)001:347: snang ba dri za'i gnas bzhin pas //
NK075(bu)001:348: khyon khang spyod yul bral ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:349: kun tu phyir rol de la med //
NK075(bu)001:350: chos kyi 'khor lo shes rab thabs //
NK075(bu)001:351: ma chags re skang 'bras bu'i gdan //
NK075(bu)001:352: ye shes du ma gcig bral bas //
NK075(bu)001:353: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin med //
NK075(bu)001:354: de na de la de gus pa //
NK075(bu)001:355: rgyal tshab rgyud dang rgyal sras sems /
NK075(bu)001:356: 'jig byed thugs rje sprul pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:357: dad pas 'brel pa brgyad sogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)001:358: de ni ston tshul 'bab pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:361: chos dbyings mu mtha' med par khyab //
NK075(bu)001:362: nor bu rin chen sku mnga' ba'i //
NK075(bu)001:363: gsang bdag de yi bdag po'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:364: tan+t+ra thugs bsdus mos bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:365: ku m+aa ra dang spyan tshor snang //
NK075(bu)001:366: de ni de yi thugs skyes phyir //
NK075(bu)001:367: de yi don ni des bsdus rigs //
NK075(bu)001:368: sku yi phye ba'i 'khor rnams la //
NK075(bu)001:369: so sor bstan pa'i dus snang yang //
NK075(bu)001:370: lhan cig pa la dus gcig snang //
NK075(bu)001:371: gang gis mthong rtogs tshe na yang //
NK075(bu)001:372: dus bzhi mnyam las ma g.yos te //
NK075(bu)001:373: de yang rang bzhin mnyam pa'i dus //
NK075(bu)001:374: rtag pa rgyun du thugs rje 'jom //
NK075(bu)001:375: mthar phyin dag pa'i dus la 'byung //
NK075(bu)001:376: de tshe rang bzhin nges lung snang //
NK075(bu)001:377: gsung lnga tshul gyis gcig la snang //
NK075(bu)001:378: mtshon byed bstan par de brjod de //
NK075(bu)001:379: de dag mtshon par rang mtshan sgra //
NK075(bu)001:380: 'gro ba gang gang gzugs brnyan yul //
NK075(bu)001:381: rigs mthun dga' 'byed mi mthun la //
NK075(bu)001:382: sgyur byed 'jigs gzugs snang ba ltar //
NK075(bu)001:383: rgyal ba'i gleng gzhi de bzhin no //
NK075(bu)001:384: de rjes rkyen gyis gling bslang ba //
NK075(bu)001:385: ston pas gnang dang 'khor gyis zhus //
NK075(bu)001:386: skabs las gleng slong ston dang 'khor //
NK075(bu)001:387: gnang 'dra'i rkyen du gang gyur pa //
NK075(bu)001:388: de des gsung la ma rag pa //
NK075(bu)001:389: nges pa'i tshig 'grub ngo bo'ang de //
NK075(bu)001:390: skabs kyi dris lan smos ci dgos //
NK075(bu)001:391: dris lan bdo bas nges par 'grub //
NK075(bu)001:392: thabs spyod shes rab gang tshe yang //
NK075(bu)001:393: rkyen byed 'byung la ma rag pas //
NK075(bu)001:394: 'khor dang gzhan gyi don phyi ru //
NK075(bu)001:396: brjod bya rang bzhin gsang ba'i rgyud //
NK075(bu)001:397: de ji bzhin du rjod byed bdag /
NK075(bu)001:398: ston pa rgyud don lam dang tshig /
NK075(bu)001:400: thabs dang thabs byung yin gyu 'bras //
NK075(bu)001:401: gleng gzhi'i rjes su nges par 'gro //
NK075(bu)001:403: me long bcu yis mtshon sbyar ba //
NK075(bu)001:404: bcu yis 'dren par shes kyis bsdu //
NK075(bu)001:405: bye brag bdag dang gzhan shes 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:406: seng chen mchongs pa'i chos gcig ltar //
NK075(bu)001:407: rnam grangs tshig lam don gcig sdud //
NK075(bu)001:408: b+y+aa g+h+ri'i mchongs pa de bzhin pas //
NK075(bu)001:409: tan+t+ra tshig don dum bur bcad //
NK075(bu)001:410: ka la ping+ka'i chos bzhi pos //
NK075(bu)001:412: rus sbal 'gros kyi chos gnyis pos //
NK075(bu)001:413: 'bru stong mi gzhag gzer bus gdab //
NK075(bu)001:414: dus kyi 'brug char chos gsum pas //
NK075(bu)001:415: bka' yi tshad gsum skabs sbyar snang //
NK075(bu)001:416: glag gi gzan gyi chos gnyis ltar //
NK075(bu)001:417: don gyi dmigs gzugs gegs bsal lo //
NK075(bu)001:418: rna phrug 'dzeg pa'i chos gnyis ltar //
NK075(bu)001:419: ldem dgongs gsang ba brgyad kyis sbyar //
NK075(bu)001:420: ngang mo'i 'gros chos rnam gnyis ltar //
NK075(bu)001:421: gzhan don dbu zhabs le mtshams sbrel //
NK075(bu)001:422: me long chos ltar mtshon pa'i dpes //
NK075(bu)001:423: kun la des mtshon thog tu dbab //
NK075(bu)001:424: mi 'jigs phru gu rtsal sbyong ltar //
NK075(bu)001:425: 'bru tshig don gyi go rim bsdeb //
NK075(bu)001:426: tshig don mos par bshad pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:427: rnam par phye bas ma 'dres gsal //
NK075(bu)001:428: thabs dang don la rang bzhin pas //
NK075(bu)001:429: tshig gis mtshon byas de snang byed //
NK075(bu)001:430: ston pa gang gis gang zhig la //
NK075(bu)001:431: gtad pa gang de ci yi phyir //
NK075(bu)001:432: rgyal sras sdud mdzad ma 'ongs sogs //
NK075(bu)001:433: mi nub bstan 'phel phyir gtad pa //
NK075(bu)001:434: shes byed yul de bsgom bya min //
NK075(bu)001:435: de yi phyi ma shes dgos med //
NK075(bu)001:437: bar du mos pas lam gzhol sdom //
NK075(bu)001:438: thun mong mchog ste tha ma gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:439: dngos spyod rjes su gzhol ba dang //
NK075(bu)001:440: pha rol phyin pa shes rab gzhol //
NK075(bu)001:441: de yang cig car rim sbyor bas //
NK075(bu)001:442: rjes su mthun pa'i lung bzhin no //
NK075(bu)001:443: lnga yi dngos spyod rjes 'brang ba //
NK075(bu)001:444: las snod skal bas phye ba la //
NK075(bu)001:445: 'tshes pa'i ngag gis dgrol byed pa //
NK075(bu)001:446: bzhi dang rang gi stobs las byung //
NK075(bu)001:447: de las khams kyi spyod pa yis //
NK075(bu)001:448: phye bas dang por lhun gnas pa //
NK075(bu)001:449: rim dang rdzogs pa'i smin tshul du //
NK075(bu)001:450: rim dang cig char snang ba ni //
NK075(bu)001:452: rang gnas sgrol ma gyen 'gro ba //
NK075(bu)001:453: de la bstan pa'i rim pa ni //
NK075(bu)001:454: bye brag bskyed pa'i cha yin no //
NK075(bu)001:455: phyi ma dbang po gsang ba gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:456: nor bu chu skyes ldan gyur pa //
NK075(bu)001:457: bcu drug bzhi rdzogs phyag rgya bzhis //
NK075(bu)001:458: kha sbyar g.yo ba'i rten gnyis la //
NK075(bu)001:459: rten dang mthun pa'i bde mthong ba //
NK075(bu)001:460: mchod pa gsum la dkyil 'khor drug /
NK075(bu)001:461: shes rab gsum gyis mig 'byang ba //
NK075(bu)001:462: rang dag mngon du mthong phyir thob //
NK075(bu)001:463: shes rab pha rol phyin sbyor ba'ang //
NK075(bu)001:464: gtso dang yan lag rnam bcu po //
NK075(bu)001:465: kun gyi don du gnyer byed pa'ang //
NK075(bu)001:466: mchog tu bya ba sngon bzhin gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:467: gcig gi blo mchog skal ldan rnams //
NK075(bu)001:468: nges par chud nas der gnas pa //
NK075(bu)001:469: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK075(bu)001:470: sems bsgom rnam gsum dus gcig rdzogs //
NK075(bu)001:471: de las ldog pa rten 'brel bzhi //
NK075(bu)001:472: lnga yi rim bstan don du gnyer //
NK075(bu)001:473: sngon du yan lag dang ba'i sdom //
NK075(bu)001:474: dgos ched thabs dang ngo bo dang //
NK075(bu)001:475: skyon dang yon tan rim pas ni //
NK075(bu)001:476: dbang po mchog ni rdzogs par bshad //
NK075(bu)001:477: gzhan pa'i lta mig bsal ba dang //
NK075(bu)001:478: mchog gi spyan rab mngon bya'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:479: lta ngan go cha rtol byed pas //
NK075(bu)001:480: the tshom med pa'i mel thud gces //
NK075(bu)001:481: gling bzhi phal ri ri bdun dang //
NK075(bu)001:482: lhun po'i gnas lta'i rim pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:483: rigs min rang bzhin ltos lta ba //
NK075(bu)001:484: phyogs sgrub mi mthun 'gegs pa dag /
NK075(bu)001:485: cha yod dug la mi reg bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:486: gang gis shes nas der mi gnas //
NK075(bu)001:487: bsam gyis mi khyab ma shes na //
NK075(bu)001:488: bsam med rnal 'byor gnyis don med //
NK075(bu)001:489: gang gis de ltar chub byas pas //
NK075(bu)001:490: stong rtogs rnal 'byor rdzogs byang chub //
NK075(bu)001:491: gang gis thog mar brten pa'i thabs //
NK075(bu)001:492: ting 'dzin bye brag las spyod dang //
NK075(bu)001:493: yan lag mang po rnam gsum gyis //
NK075(bu)001:494: gtan tshigs thun mong yin min pa //
NK075(bu)001:495: rgyud las grags pas rkyen byas te //
NK075(bu)001:496: ri rgyal lta bur mthong bar gces //
NK075(bu)001:497: rgyu rkyen gang gis nges skyes pa //
NK075(bu)001:498: the tshom yid gnyis som nyi ba //
NK075(bu)001:499: med la brjod kyi ngos rtog med //
NK075(bu)001:500: dgag sgrub med kyi rgyud las byung //
NK075(bu)001:501: dbang po drug gis 'char snang yang //
NK075(bu)001:502: spyan la mchog tu brjod pa ni //
NK075(bu)001:503: shes rab yul du dbyer med pas //
NK075(bu)001:504: mngon sum rtogs pas rtogs pa'i mchog /
NK075(bu)001:505: rang rig ye shes tshogs gcig po //
NK075(bu)001:506: shes rab spyan gyi dam pa bas //
NK075(bu)001:507: de la phyi nang med pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:508: chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mthong //
NK075(bu)001:509: de lta'ang log rtog ma zad pas //
NK075(bu)001:510: 'khor sgyur rgyal po'i stobs bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:511: rang mtshan mthong yang de lta bas //
NK075(bu)001:512: dbang bsgyur rigs dang khyad par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:513: gsang ba'i rgyud las 'di skad du //
NK075(bu)001:514: lta dang blta bar bya med pa'i //
NK075(bu)001:515: ye shes sgron me 'greng bar ni //
NK075(bu)001:516: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad mthong //
NK075(bu)001:517: de bas ci la gang zhig zhen //
NK075(bu)001:518: gsang sngags yid yul gang gis rnyed //
NK075(bu)001:519: rdo rje yid kyi sgras gol bas //
NK075(bu)001:520: 'dus ma byas la dmigs pa dag /
NK075(bu)001:522: rjes la rnal 'byor mi rtog ces //
NK075(bu)001:523: phyogs nas mthun par bskyed 'dod pa //
NK075(bu)001:525: kun tu rgyu dang gzhon nu ltar //
NK075(bu)001:526: go mchog thos pa'i khyad par ni //
NK075(bu)001:527: rigs brgyad bcu lnga'i rtsa ba las //
NK075(bu)001:528: lta ba'i khyad par gsungs pa yin //
NK075(bu)001:529: rnam grangs dam pa'i sgras gol ba //
NK075(bu)001:530: de yi sgra la ji bzhin rtog /
NK075(bu)001:531: de min mthun par ldog byed pa //
NK075(bu)001:532: dbul po lta ba nyid kho na //
NK075(bu)001:533: bzhi pa 'di skad lung las byung //
NK075(bu)001:534: thabs la mkhas pas ma zin na //
NK075(bu)001:535: lam gyi dge spyod stegs byas kyang //
NK075(bu)001:536: mtho ris lha dang mi ru skye //
NK075(bu)001:537: skye shi med pa'i sa mi thob //
NK075(bu)001:538: lnga pa ji skad 'byung zhe na //
NK075(bu)001:539: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ni //
NK075(bu)001:540: dang po don rtog mthar mi gtong //
NK075(bu)001:541: chu srin phyag rgya ji bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:542: spyod yul kun tu tshad dpag med //
NK075(bu)001:543: de rjes gtso mchog goms byed pa //
NK075(bu)001:545: rang gi yan lag rdzogs pa yi //
NK075(bu)001:546: gang du 'du shes med gsal ba //
NK075(bu)001:547: gang dag bcu dang ldan pa yi //
NK075(bu)001:548: snga ma las kyang gnas 'gyur ro //
NK075(bu)001:549: 'pho ba med par bzhis snang bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:550: de yi yan lag de bzhin pas //
NK075(bu)001:551: rgyu las thob par rang gnas pa //
NK075(bu)001:552: snang ba kun tu khyab pa ni //
NK075(bu)001:553: phyi nang med par mthu rdzogs bya //
NK075(bu)001:554: de yi stobs las skyes pa ni //
NK075(bu)001:556: tshig shes skye ba ji bzhin pa //
NK075(bu)001:557: gnyis la gang mos gnyis tshul gyis //
NK075(bu)001:558: bzhi pa dgu dang ldan pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:559: rang gi cha rkyen tshang ba yis //
NK075(bu)001:560: de la zhen pa grol 'gyur zhing //
NK075(bu)001:561: bzhi lnga ldan nas ldang bar bya //
NK075(bu)001:562: gang smin mthun pa'i rgyud 'phel zhing //
NK075(bu)001:563: de yi bzhi las tshangs ya ma'i //
NK075(bu)001:564: gzugs can spros par rang gnas te //
NK075(bu)001:565: rgya mtsho gza' dang skar ma dang //
NK075(bu)001:566: 'brel bzhin rdo rje cho gas sam //
NK075(bu)001:567: bslab pa rang gi rkyen tshang ba //
NK075(bu)001:568: lung bcu ldan nas de spro'am //
NK075(bu)001:569: yang na de nas longs spyod sbyar //
NK075(bu)001:572: de dang mi 'tshams longs spyod lnga //
NK075(bu)001:573: rang gi bzhi bzhi thabs bzhi dang //
NK075(bu)001:574: ldan pas grangs tshad rtags byung na //
NK075(bu)001:575: dkyil 'khor mthun sbyar thabs gnyis so //
NK075(bu)001:576: yan lag tshang na zag pa med //
NK075(bu)001:577: de min lan grangs gzhan nyid du'o //
NK075(bu)001:578: rgya mtshor rin chen bzhi yi 'od //
NK075(bu)001:579: phog pa ji bzhin thob 'gyur yang //
NK075(bu)001:580: 'dis ni thar lam rim sbyar na //
NK075(bu)001:581: sangs rgyas sa la gdon mi za //
NK075(bu)001:582: yan lag gnyis pa 'dir shes te //
NK075(bu)001:583: de dag las su rang byed pa //
NK075(bu)001:584: dgos ched rnam grangs dus dang ni //
NK075(bu)001:585: skyon dang yon tan sdom gyis rdzogs //
NK075(bu)001:586: bdag dang gzhan gyi don gyi phyir //
NK075(bu)001:587: dbyi sogs mi gos goms pa gces //
NK075(bu)001:588: gsang rgyud nyid las gsungs pa yi //
NK075(bu)001:589: barlunga po dam rdzas sha spyod pa //
NK075(bu)001:590: 'dod yon nyon mongs nyi shu lnga //
NK075(bu)001:591: nag pos 'dul ba ji snyed pa //
NK075(bu)001:592: thun mong min te de bzlog dkar //
NK075(bu)001:593: khyad par lam dang sar mthun pa'o //
NK075(bu)001:594: zhen pa'i lam la de nyid de //
NK075(bu)001:595: ji ltar dug la dug nag bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:596: bdag dang gzhan pa gnyis ka la'ang //
NK075(bu)001:597: tshe dang mkhas pa'i thabs kyis spyod //
NK075(bu)001:598: gcig shes pa de dmangs rje dang //
NK075(bu)001:599: bram ze rgyal po lnga rim bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:600: shes par bslab bya mang po kun //
NK075(bu)001:601: btson pa dor ba yod ma yin //
NK075(bu)001:602: de goms mtshon pa gnyis pa ltar //
NK075(bu)001:603: 'jug pa gsum la yid tshang thabs //
NK075(bu)001:604: cha mthun gdams ngag byings rgod de //
NK075(bu)001:605: 'bru sogs rim dang bzlog la brten //
NK075(bu)001:606: gtsang ma rigs kyi mthu bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:607: mthong goms bzhi 'dus spyod yul sbyong //
NK075(bu)001:608: lnga par sri zhu rgyal chos ni //
NK075(bu)001:609: dang po bzhin du longs spyod lnga //
NK075(bu)001:610: shin tu spros spyod blang bar bya //
NK075(bu)001:611: lnga par lnga po gtso bo yin //
NK075(bu)001:612: de nas bzhi yi zag bral nas //
NK075(bu)001:613: lcags zangs gser dngul go rim bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:614: bdag gzhan yul gyi khyad par 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:615: snga ma rgyud ldan rtsol ba med //
NK075(bu)001:616: rang rang bslab pa gang yin pa //
NK075(bu)001:617: skabs su gces pa khyad par yin //
NK075(bu)001:618: lam dang pa yi rim sbyar nas //
NK075(bu)001:619: spyod par grags la re tshed pa //
NK075(bu)001:620: snga ma goms mthar phyin 'jug tshe //
NK075(bu)001:621: de nas rang gi spyod yul blang //
NK075(bu)001:622: khyad par dor ba mthar phyin med //
NK075(bu)001:623: barlanga pa rang gang spyod pa ni //
NK075(bu)001:624: don du mi 'gyur bzhin dbang bas //
NK075(bu)001:625: so so'i rnam smin tshad las 'das //
NK075(bu)001:626: de la de yi de yod phyir //
NK075(bu)001:627: de nges gnyis po mi lhung thob //
NK075(bu)001:628: so so'i ltung thob grags pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:630: bya ba'i sdom ni dgos ched dang //
NK075(bu)001:631: ngo bo nges tshig rnam grangs dang //
NK075(bu)001:632: bya thabs skabs dang khyad par dang //
NK075(bu)001:633: skyon yon dgu yis rdzogs pa yin //
NK075(bu)001:634: bdag dang gzhan dang gnyis ka dang //
NK075(bu)001:635: dam chos phyir na rnam lnga'o //
NK075(bu)001:636: shing la chu bzhin dang blang ba //
NK075(bu)001:637: rab 'bring tha ma nus tshad sbyar //
NK075(bu)001:638: gdul bya phyi nang zung bzhi po //
NK075(bu)001:639: gdul ba'i mthu chen rnam bzhi dang //
NK075(bu)001:640: gcig gis kun 'dul mthu can sogs //
NK075(bu)001:641: lnga po gang yin de ngo bo //
NK075(bu)001:642: zug rngu phyi nang zhi phyir dang //
NK075(bu)001:644: 'gugs dbang bzhi po sdud phyir dang //
NK075(bu)001:645: gdug pa rnam gnyis 'jams phyir dang //
NK075(bu)001:646: lnga pa sngon du bstan bzhin phyir //
NK075(bu)001:647: nges tshig nges par 'grub pa yin //
NK075(bu)001:648: don gyi dmigs su gzung ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:649: rang bzhin lam du thugs rjes phye //
NK075(bu)001:650: bar ma thabs dang shes rab la //
NK075(bu)001:651: snga ma gnyis dang phyi ma la //
NK075(bu)001:652: shes rab ting 'dzin rnam gnyis dang //
NK075(bu)001:653: longs spyod lhag pa gzugs brnyan gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:654: de la phyi nang gsang bar bshad //
NK075(bu)001:655: ngo bo rjes su zhi ba gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:656: phyi la bgegs dgra zhi ba'o //
NK075(bu)001:657: nang la nyon mongs rtog zhi ba'o //
NK075(bu)001:658: rgyas pa gnyis po gso dang 'phel //
NK075(bu)001:660: tshe dang longs spyod rigs brgyud dang //
NK075(bu)001:661: bsod nams bzhi po nang 'bras bu //
NK075(bu)001:662: dbang ni dgug dang bsdu ba gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:663: phyi rol d+ha r+ai'i rnam pa dgug /
NK075(bu)001:664: mi mthun rnam gnyis dbang po gyur //
NK075(bu)001:665: rang sems 'bras lnga bsdu bar bya //
NK075(bu)001:666: mngon spyod bskrad dang mnan pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:667: smyo 'bogs byad dang skem pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:668: rmongs dang brtan g.yo rgyud gzhan la'o //
NK075(bu)001:669: rang gi phyi nang dgra bgegs 'jams //
NK075(bu)001:670: thabs ni thabs la gsang ba nang //
NK075(bu)001:671: khams bzhi khams gsum la sbyar bya //
NK075(bu)001:672: shes rab phyi nang gnyis kyi ste //
NK075(bu)001:673: phyi rol tshad med nyid las bzhi //
NK075(bu)001:674: lhag pa gzugs brnyan bya thabs gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:675: mchod rten sgo dang sbyin sreg ste //
NK075(bu)001:676: phyi ma gnas dang sgrub po dang //
NK075(bu)001:677: thab brgyad 'brub khang bcas pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:678: phyogs dang kha dog dus nyid dang //
NK075(bu)001:679: phur pa lha dang sems dang yum //
NK075(bu)001:680: bsgrub bya'i ling+ga me mchod dang //
NK075(bu)001:681: dkyil 'khor yo byad tshang bar sbyar //
NK075(bu)001:682: bya thabs gtso bo sbyin sreg la //
NK075(bu)001:683: skabs su dgos pa ling+ga gdab //
NK075(bu)001:684: bro stabs bcas pa'i cha rkyen no //
NK075(bu)001:685: de dag rtsa ba'i mchod brnyes dang //
NK075(bu)001:686: tan gon me mchod sbyin sreg rim //
NK075(bu)001:687: smon lam lhag ma'i las dag go //
NK075(bu)001:688: skabs ni dbang dang sgrub pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:689: mchod bshags tshe dang dus bab tshe //
NK075(bu)001:690: khyad par zag bcas bar chad med //
NK075(bu)001:691: mthar phyin lam gyi rim pa'am //
NK075(bu)001:692: shes rab dbang po rnam gsum gyi //
NK075(bu)001:693: nus mthu byin rlabs yul ngo bo //
NK075(bu)001:694: thabs dang gzhi dang khyad par la //
NK075(bu)001:695: skas kyi gdang bu ji lta'o //
NK075(bu)001:696: mi skong mi 'byong mi rdzogs dang //
NK075(bu)001:697: don gnyis mi 'grub de yi skyon //
NK075(bu)001:698: de las ldog pa'i tshul ldan pa //
NK075(bu)001:699: yon tan nyid du shes par bya //
NK075(bu)001:700: sa bzhi sdom ni ngo bo grangs //
NK075(bu)001:701: dgos ched dus dang che ba dang //
NK075(bu)001:702: yon tan bskang thabs skyon dag gis //
NK075(bu)001:703: nges par dmigs su shes par bya //
NK075(bu)001:704: gsang sgor zhugs pa thams cad kyi //
NK075(bu)001:705: sgo gsum rang gi bsrung bya las //
NK075(bu)001:706: rgyal po bka' rtags ji lta bar //
NK075(bu)001:707: mi 'bral sdom pa de ngo bo //
NK075(bu)001:708: thun mong gzhung gzhan 'gro don du //
NK075(bu)001:709: khyad par rtsa ba yan lag ste //
NK075(bu)001:710: mdo rgyas rab 'bring tha yi grangs //
NK075(bu)001:711: tan+t+rara gsung ba brnyad par bya //
NK075(bu)001:712: theg chen sa lam khyad par bya //
NK075(bu)001:713: skabs kyi lam chos mi mthun bsrung //
NK075(bu)001:714: de yi dgos ched rang dang spyi //
NK075(bu)001:715: skyon yon cha yis ched che ba //
NK075(bu)001:716: de dang de yis nges tshig 'grub //
NK075(bu)001:717: rang spyi'i gdul bya'i sbyang bsags pa'i //
NK075(bu)001:718: bsrung bya'i rim pa yod pa'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:719: sa lam gang thob de yi tshe //
NK075(bu)001:720: de la de dgos de bsrung ba //
NK075(bu)001:721: skabs dang sbyar na phan yon gnyis //
NK075(bu)001:722: bsrung bya mchog la bskul ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:723: smos pa bla med bsrung thub na //
NK075(bu)001:724: tshul khrims sdom pa thams cad rdzogs //
NK075(bu)001:725: bya byed med par nyams pa'ang med //
NK075(bu)001:726: ma nor gnas pa'i phan yon ni //
NK075(bu)001:727: rnam grangs rjes zhugs phyi rgyud grags //
NK075(bu)001:728: gzung dang thob pa'i dbye ba'ang bya //
NK075(bu)001:729: bdag dang gzhan dgos grangs rdzogs pa'o //
NK075(bu)001:730: de de zhig ral byung ba yi //
NK075(bu)001:731: dmigs shes gso ba'i rtsa ba lnga //
NK075(bu)001:732: le lo med par chos lcogs sbyar //
NK075(bu)001:733: des na nges par rdzogs gzungs thob //
NK075(bu)001:734: myal ba le lo log pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:735: zlas zhar nyon mongs dbang song dang //
NK075(bu)001:736: bdud kyis bslus dang rang bzhin ngan //
NK075(bu)001:737: brgyad rgyus dka' thub ral ba dag /
NK075(bu)001:738: dus 'di phyi mar drag zhan gyis //
NK075(bu)001:739: spyi dang sgos skyon gnyis la gnod //
NK075(bu)001:740: bkod pa rgyal las bdun gsungs pa //
NK075(bu)001:741: sdom ni ngo bo khyad par grangs //
NK075(bu)001:742: dgos pa thabs dang dus nges tshig /
NK075(bu)001:743: yon tan skyon gyi gzhi ru bzhag /
NK075(bu)001:744: gnas skabs bdun dang snying po len //
NK075(bu)001:745: bkod pa gang rdzogs de ngo bo //
NK075(bu)001:746: dang po ngang bzhin nyid mthar phyin //
NK075(bu)001:747: gdul byas zhi dang khro bo de //
NK075(bu)001:748: mos pas sku gsung thugs yon tan //
NK075(bu)001:749: phrin las gtso bas phye ba lnga //
NK075(bu)001:750: rtsa ba de yang skabs kyis grangs //
NK075(bu)001:751: mchod pa dbang dang phrin las sgrub //
NK075(bu)001:752: gzhi yang gtso bos grangs rjes mthun //
NK075(bu)001:753: kun la 'jug pas bcu bzhi dang //
NK075(bu)001:754: sum cu rtsa lngar 'gyur ba yin //
NK075(bu)001:755: de yi rjes su drug sbyar ba'o //
NK075(bu)001:756: bzhi po dus su bdag gzhan phyir //
NK075(bu)001:757: dran dang rten dang 'brel ba dang //
NK075(bu)001:758: bsgom dang bsgrub sogs mchod bsgrub phyir //
NK075(bu)001:759: shin tu nan tan blang bar bya //
NK075(bu)001:760: sa yi bya ba'i rim pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:761: de yi cho ga'i thabs dag ni //
NK075(bu)001:762: rang bzhin la sogs bdun dag la //
NK075(bu)001:763: gang la yod pa kun yod de //
NK075(bu)001:764: thabs dang shes rab las kyis bya //
NK075(bu)001:766: bdun gyi gtso snying gang gang la //
NK075(bu)001:767: de yi 'khor ldan nges pa'i tshig /
NK075(bu)001:768: lung las grags pas the tshom med //
NK075(bu)001:769: tha dad gcig gis bcings dang bral //
NK075(bu)001:771: bye brag so so'i grangs bzhin no //
NK075(bu)001:772: de las ldog pa'i skyon cha ni //
NK075(bu)001:773: grangs kyi rjes su nges par 'gro //
NK075(bu)001:774: mnyes par byed pa'i sdom tshig ni //
NK075(bu)001:775: dgos tshe ngo bo grangs skabs dang //
NK075(bu)001:776: skyon dang yon tan la sogs pas //
NK075(bu)001:777: ji lta ba bzhin shes par bya //
NK075(bu)001:778: bdag gzhan don rdzogs mnyes bskangs pa //
NK075(bu)001:779: 'di dang phyi mar thob pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:780: yon tan bka' las gsungs pa bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:781: chad skyon mi 'byung bya phyir ro //
NK075(bu)001:782: bya byed bya ba byed 'dus pa //
NK075(bu)001:783: dges tshim 'gyur ba'i dngos po nyid //
NK075(bu)001:784: 'jig rten spyod mthun mos bya'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:785: phyag dang phyag rgya glu gar tshig /
NK075(bu)001:786: phyi nang gsang ba'i rdzas dgongs mchod //
NK075(bu)001:787: srog dang ldan pas bden gsum tshul //
NK075(bu)001:788: mchod pa gsum las spros pa dag /
NK075(bu)001:789: dkyil 'khor bdun gyi gnas dag la //
NK075(bu)001:790: dbul phyir dgos ched rjes zhugs pas //
NK075(bu)001:791: las spyod bsgrub dbang mchod tshe na'o //
NK075(bu)001:792: dus kyi rjes zhugs yon tan dag /
NK075(bu)001:793: spyi dang khyad par dus kyis na //
NK075(bu)001:794: 'di dang phyi mar gang thob pa //
NK075(bu)001:795: bdag gzhan don gyis gnyis su 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:796: de las ldog dang mi skong g.yel //
NK075(bu)001:797: nyams chad mthu byin bral bar 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:798: thob par bya ba'i sdom tshig ni //
NK075(bu)001:799: dgos ched rgyu rkyen ngo bo grangs //
NK075(bu)001:800: thabs dang thob tshad dus snod dang //
NK075(bu)001:801: yon tan skyon dang dkyil 'khor sbyangs //
NK075(bu)001:802: don 'gyur bzhi la khyad par du //
NK075(bu)001:803: bdag gzhan don nus tshogs las 'grub //
NK075(bu)001:804: byang dang chub par gyur par myur //
NK075(bu)001:805: de la de yong phyir nang bya //
NK075(bu)001:806: lung dang man ngag las byung ba'i //
NK075(bu)001:807: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi'i yan lag brnyad //
NK075(bu)001:808: drug la gnas pa'i thob bya ste //
NK075(bu)001:809: ngo bo nyid ces rnam par bshad //
NK075(bu)001:810: rtsa ba rnam la lnga bco brgyad //
NK075(bu)001:811: bsgyur ba lnga la sum cu drug /
NK075(bu)001:812: dkyil 'khor las kyi rjes zhugs pas //
NK075(bu)001:813: snod rim sbyar ba'i las rdzogs sbyor //
NK075(bu)001:814: rno la til mar ngar rim bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:815: nus mthu gzhan la nges par bzhag /
NK075(bu)001:816: lam gyi shes rab sngon 'gro ba //
NK075(bu)001:817: thabs la de nyid rim par bslab //
NK075(bu)001:818: gnyis ka sa yi dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK075(bu)001:819: dang po dred rnyed mi ldog pa'i //
NK075(bu)001:820: rim pa'i las rig ye shes rgya //
NK075(bu)001:821: rim par rol pa rgyud nyid las //
NK075(bu)001:822: dad brtson gsum dang brtul zhugs gsum //
NK075(bu)001:823: gang la yod pa de yi snod //
NK075(bu)001:824: 'di dang phyi ma'i phan yon grangs //
NK075(bu)001:825: rgyud nas gsungs pa ji bzhin te //
NK075(bu)001:826: de ldog rang byan chos nyid dang //
NK075(bu)001:827: gsung ba nyams pas ltung 'jigs pa //
NK075(bu)001:828: so ma btang ba'i rdza spyod ltar //
NK075(bu)001:829: 'gyur ba gsang ba'i rgyud kun ltos //
NK075(bu)001:830: don du gnyer ba thob bya yis //
NK075(bu)001:831: phye ba gnyis sogs sdom pa'i tshig /
NK075(bu)001:832: dgos ched ngo bo grangs thabs dang //
NK075(bu)001:833: dus dang skyon yon grangs shes bya //
NK075(bu)001:834: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NK075(bu)001:835: bdag gzhan thob nas don bzhi'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:836: gang gis gang thob 'dod pa de //
NK075(bu)001:837: yan lag bcu ldan gnyer bdo ba'i //
NK075(bu)001:838: mngon shes tshe dang rdzu 'phrul las //
NK075(bu)001:839: sku gsung thugs kyi thun mong dag /
NK075(bu)001:840: sgrub thabs mi mthun grags pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:841: zag med 'bras bu mchog lnga po //
NK075(bu)001:842: sgrub pa'i thabs su grags pa kun //
NK075(bu)001:843: phun sum tshogs pa bzhi ldan nas //
NK075(bu)001:844: brtags shing byin gyis brlabs pa der //
NK075(bu)001:845: tshogs bskyed bsnyen sgrub grangs dus mtshan //
NK075(bu)001:846: so sor phye ba brgyad gsungs bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:848: sngags dang phyag rgya brtan pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:849: mi lcog med par gang yod dang //
NK075(bu)001:850: cha rkyen tshang ba mngon bsgyur mngon //
NK075(bu)001:851: yal ba'i mi 'byang mi thob bcu //
NK075(bu)001:852: bye brag rgyas pa khong du chud //
NK075(bu)001:853: de las ldog pa 'di phyi mar //
NK075(bu)001:854: lnga lnga thob pas don gnyis rdzogs //
NK075(bu)001:855: sngags dang phyag rgya'i sdom tshig ni //
NK075(bu)001:856: dgos ched ngo bo grangs thabs dang //
NK075(bu)001:857: nges tshig gang du dgos pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:858: yon tan skyon dang spyod yul bshad //
NK075(bu)001:859: sbyang gzhi nye bar bsnyen pa dang //
NK075(bu)001:860: thob bya lnga po rdzogs bya'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:861: gnyis ka'i ched du shin tu gces //
NK075(bu)001:862: yi ge 'dus pa grub pa bzhi'i //
NK075(bu)001:863: mthu chen red pa gang yin pa //
NK075(bu)001:864: bzhi rdzogs gnyis las mi 'da' ba //
NK075(bu)001:865: gang la snang ba de ngo bo //
NK075(bu)001:866: rig gsang gzungs sngags shes bya ba //
NK075(bu)001:867: rtsa bskyed las rim las bsnyen dang //
NK075(bu)001:868: mchod pa dang ni rgya bzhi las //
NK075(bu)001:869: chen po rang bzhin ting 'dzin dang //
NK075(bu)001:870: mtshon pa mtshan ma'i phyag rgya dang //
NK075(bu)001:871: yul dang 'dzin bsam bca' ba'i dam //
NK075(bu)001:872: bsam dang bca' dang rang bzhin dang //
NK075(bu)001:874: bde ba rang bzhin bzlas bsam dag /
NK075(bu)001:875: lam gyis phye bas grangs mang ngo //
NK075(bu)001:876: skyon bcu le lo dor ba dang //
NK075(bu)001:877: skyon brgyad spang ba'i brtson pas sbyangs //
NK075(bu)001:878: mthu byin ldan zhing don mi 'da' //
NK075(bu)001:879: de phyir ming gi sgra 'jug go //
NK075(bu)001:880: dkyil 'khor dgod pa'i dus lnga dang //
NK075(bu)001:881: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi'i tshe na'o //
NK075(bu)001:882: sngags dang phyag rgya rab brtan na //
NK075(bu)001:883: dngos grub ya mtshan che bar 'gyur //
NK075(bu)001:884: yid la bsam pa thams cad 'grub //
NK075(bu)001:885: ral gri'i so la bzung nyes ltar //
NK075(bu)001:886: nan tan med pa'i gsang sngags pa //
NK075(bu)001:888: gsang ba gsum la mos rim bzhin //
NK075(bu)001:889: gang la spyod pa de yul lo //
NK075(bu)001:890: tha mar rig pa'i drod tshad pa //
NK075(bu)001:891: nye bar sbyor ba sa de ni //
NK075(bu)001:892: rang gi sgrub dang ting 'dzin sdom //
NK075(bu)001:893: zag med lam sbyor tshogs gnyis grangs //
NK075(bu)001:894: thabs dang shes rab ting 'dzin grangs //
NK075(bu)001:895: tshad ma gnyis las grags pa dag /
NK075(bu)001:896: legs sbyang thob nas zag pa med //
NK075(bu)001:897: thigs pa tha ma snga ma'i rgyus //
NK075(bu)001:898: thob pa'i sdom tshig lam mthar phyin //
NK075(bu)001:899: bde gshegs rgyal ba nyid yin no //
NK075(bu)001:900: de phyir bcu yis 'bru sbyar te //
NK075(bu)001:901: rus sbal brtul zhugs blang bar bya //
NK075(bu)001:902: de yul byas pa rnyed don 'dus //
NK075(bu)001:904: gdul bya dag pa'i snang ba'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NK075(bu)001:905: rdo rje yan lag bzhi pa'i sdom //
NK075(bu)001:906: mtshan nyid tha ma lung bstan pa //
NK075(bu)001:907: rig pa 'dzin dang rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK075(bu)001:908: snga ma thob tshul rnam grangs dang //
NK075(bu)001:909: nges tshig gnas su rnam par bshad //
NK075(bu)001:910: lhag ma yod med 'da' tshul gyis //
NK075(bu)001:911: 'di dang bar mar rnam par sbyor //
NK075(bu)001:912: rnam par smin pa bya gcan tshul //
NK075(bu)001:913: dbang bsgyur phung po 'jig pa med //
NK075(bu)001:914: phyag rgya chen por bdag lus snang //
NK075(bu)001:915: nyi shu lngar grub rang snang ba //
NK075(bu)001:916: de la de yi rtsol ba can //
NK075(bu)001:917: me chu rlung gi rigs gnas shing //
NK075(bu)001:918: gang rig zin pa mi gtong ba //
NK075(bu)001:919: dang po byung dang bya byed dang //
NK075(bu)001:921: de yi gzhugs gnas nges med de //
NK075(bu)001:922: sems rig gnas snang gang yang rung //
NK075(bu)001:923: bya ba byas pa'i grub pa dag /
NK075(bu)001:924: thob tshul ngo bo 'bras bu grangs //
NK075(bu)001:925: spyod yul gzigs dang thugs rjes sprul //
NK075(bu)001:926: mdzad pa ye shes bzhugs tshul sdom //
NK075(bu)001:927: bdag gi dbang du 'di skad du //
NK075(bu)001:928: dpag bsam shing dang rin po che //
NK075(bu)001:929: de dag rdzas yod ma yin te //
NK075(bu)001:930: rang sems bsod nams brtan pa yin //
NK075(bu)001:931: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK075(bu)001:932: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK075(bu)001:933: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK075(bu)001:934: de lta bu yi ngang du byung //
NK075(bu)001:935: gzhan gyi don du 'di skad du //
NK075(bu)001:936: bya ba ma lus kun byas nas //
NK075(bu)001:937: mthar ni skye med rdo rje'i sa //
NK075(bu)001:938: gsungs pa srid pa tha ma dang //
NK075(bu)001:939: rdo rje 'dzin sku rdor gsum las //
NK075(bu)001:940: sprul pa drug gi dbang po yin //
NK075(bu)001:941: mdzad pa rdzogs nas sangs rgyas tshul //
NK075(bu)001:942: gsang ba'i skabs la shes par bya //
NK075(bu)001:943: gnyis med sems su mngon byas pa //
NK075(bu)001:944: bden gnyis dbyer med rdo rje'i sku //
NK075(bu)001:945: chu yi zla ba lta bu la //
NK075(bu)001:946: rang bzhin kun dang tha mi dad //
NK075(bu)001:947: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan las //
NK075(bu)001:948: rgyan gyi 'khor lo rang bzhin gnas //
NK075(bu)001:949: thams cad mkhyen yul 'di skad du //
NK075(bu)001:950: log par rtog brtags rnam dag cing //
NK075(bu)001:951: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK075(bu)001:952: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na //
NK075(bu)001:953: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK075(bu)001:954: rnam par rtog pa mi mnga' ste //
NK075(bu)001:955: de yis mi mkhyen gang yang med //
NK075(bu)001:956: me long lta bu'i tshul bzhin du //
NK075(bu)001:957: sna tshogs kha dog dbyibs su snang //
NK075(bu)001:958: bde gshegs rang bzhin thams cad phyir //
NK075(bu)001:961: de yod na ni gzung 'dzin can //
NK075(bu)001:962: sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor sgrol ba yis //
NK075(bu)001:963: bya byed med pa'i dkyil 'khor spyod //
NK075(bu)001:964: dus gsum rim par rdzogs sangs pa'i //
NK075(bu)001:965: log rtog tha dad dag pa yang //
NK075(bu)001:966: ye nas mtha' las grol ba'i phyir //
NK075(bu)001:967: gcig dang mi gcig brjod bsam 'das //
NK075(bu)001:968: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK075(bu)001:969: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK075(bu)001:970: rgyud las gsungs pas bgrod dang bla //
NK075(bu)001:971: rgya mtsho chu dang rlabs bzhin no //
NK075(bu)001:973: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //
NK075(bu)001:975: // mkha' la gzha' bzhin rgyud don bkra gsal 'dis //
NK075(bu)001:976: mi shes nga rgyal snyoms shing nyon mongs dgra las rgyal //
NK075(bu)001:977: dpa' bo'i ru mtshon gnam lcags shak+ti 'dra //
NK075(bu)001:978: rgyud kyi don bcud 'khor lo dang mchu ltar blangs pas //
NK075(bu)001:979: mi shes d+r+wa bar chud rnams gsang ba'i snying por shog //
NK075(bu)001:980: thugs kyi thigs pa sgyu 'phrul spyi gcod rdzogs so //
